- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is also likely as the paper proposes a new numerical method for computing distance. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper discusses applications in computer graphics such as shape matching and deformation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper mentions applications in image processing and object recognition. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper discusses the efficiency and complexity of the proposed method.
